org.objectweb.asm.jip.attrs
Class StackMapFrame

java.lang.Object
  org.objectweb.asm.jip.attrs.StackMapFrame

public class StackMapFrame
extends java.lang.Object

Holds the state of the stack and local variables for a single execution branch. Note that Long and Double types are represented by two entries in locals and stack. Second entry should be always of type Top.

Eugene Kuleshov
